metadata.name: Part Of Existence
metadata.description:
She is the one who transfers her whole being and the sap of her existence to her child so that the child grows.
The child is a part of the mother and protects her from all dangers. All the dangers that this mother can sense in the world around her... This woman has a very big mind and is aware of everything. She knows what dangers her child may face during childhood and adulthood. When the mother of this child feels the dangers, she becomes very strong and warrior against the dangers
4069 x 3669 px
